      • RideFinished

        public double RideFinished(Ride ride,
                           int mark)
        When a ride is finished, we use this method to change car's, driver's, customer's and ride's state. At the same time, we update the total ride number and money cashed for the customer and the driver. Then we give the car and the customer in this ride a new GPS location for the next ride. We also change the driver's state after a ride(from on-a-ride to on-duty or take a break or offline). We need to manually change a driver's status from off-duty to on-duty/
        Parameters:
        ride -
        Returns:
